data.eml:eml: A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from Gunung Mulu National Park, Sarawak, East Malaysia (Borneo)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dehling, J. Maximilian, Matsui, Masafumi (2013): A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from Gunung Mulu National Park, Sarawak, East Malaysia (Borneo). Zootaxa 3670 (1): 33-44, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3670.1.2
